---
import Accordion from "@/components/ui/Accordion.astro";
---

<section
  id="faq"
  class="border-border from-primary/50 scroll-mt-24 border-t bg-gradient-to-br to-white"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-20">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">
      Questions? We&apos;ve Got Answers!
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <Accordion
        items={[
          {
            title: "What does it mean to stake money on a goal?",
            content:
              "When you create a goal, you lock in a stake. If you finish and prove it, you keep your money. " +
              "If you fail or can’t verify, the stake is charged — simple as that.",
          },
          {
            title: "Do I ever win money?",
            content:
              "Yes — but only in group challenges or if you’re a designated recipient. In group mode, if you " +
              "finish and others fail, you share the stakes they lost. If someone sets you as the destination " +
              "for failed stakes, you also receive those funds.",
          },
          {
            title: "How do I prove I completed a goal?",
            content:
              "Each goal uses one verification method: motion detection for activity tracking, in-app photos for visual proof, " +
              "or simple time-based check-ins. Choose the method that best fits your specific goal.",
          },
          {
            title: "What happens if I can’t verify but still did it?",
            content:
              "Without proof, it counts as a fail. Stakes only work if verification is strict — so always make" +
              " sure to log evidence.",
          },
          {
            title: "Who verifies my proof?",
            content:
              "Proof is first checked automatically when possible (like motion data or timestamps). If needed, " +
              "trained reviewers step in to validate submissions. Reviewers are vetted and approved by us to " +
              "ensure fairness.",
          },
          {
            title: "How are payments handled?",
            content:
              "All payments are processed securely via Stripe in CHF (Swiss francs). Your stake is only charged " +
              "if you fail to complete or verify your goal. Captured funds go to the configured destination " +
              "(like charity, a pool, or a designated recipient).",
          },
          {
            title: "Does this work on iOS and Android?",
            content:
              "Yes — the app is built with Expo and works on both platforms at launch.",
          },
        ]}
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
